## 🏗️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/babyTic/gestion-conges-anptic.git
cd gestion-conges-anptic
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate
php artisan serve
npm run dev 

👉 Accès : http://127.0.0.1:8000

